<author>hạny̱ ftḥy, rạỷd gẖbryạl</author>
<title>ạ̉ḥbk ạ̉bạrkk yạ sydy</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- ạ̉ḥbk .. ạ̉bạrkk yạ sydy
 ạ̉ʿẓmk ạ̉mjdk .. fạ̉nt kl sẖyʾ ly
 1- ạ̉nt hw ạ̉by ạlḥbyb .. rạfʿ rạ̉sy ʿạḍdy
 yswʿ qd kẖlṣtny .. ʿmạnwỷyl ạ̉nt mʿy
 2- ạ̉nt hw nbʿ ạlḥyạẗ .. lmsẗ ydyk fyhạ sẖfạʾ
 ạ̹ly̱ mn yạ rby ạ̉dẖhb .. wʿndk nbʿ ạrtwạʾ
 3- ạ̉nt hw ạlạ̉lf wạlyạʾ .. mnk bk kl ạlạ̉sẖyạʾ
 ạ̉msaⁿạ wạlywm llạ̉bd .. syẓl rwḥk ʿạḍdy</lyrics>
</song>